# Juml Authors

Juml is copyright (c) 2015-2026 naou and contributors.

This file lists the people and organizations who have contributed to Juml.
Names are added in the order in which contributions were made.

- naou (maintainer)

Contributions are welcome. See CONTRIBUTING.md for details. The full list of
contributors is also available from the project's Git history and the GitHub
contributors page: https://github.com/nigoh/juml/graphs/contributors
